jailmap including race (automatic kill), gun toss , deagle roulette, football, last man standing room ( with automatic heal when game starts/ends), many walkable buildings, elevator,many secret places/teleportes/tunnels/weapons, Weapon Boxes only Ct can open ( for last resort ) etc etc...

Camera system with portable Monitor !
